<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        h1 { color: #6c757d; } /* Grey */
        p { line-height: 1.6; }
        .message-box { background-color: #f8f9fa; border: 1px solid #e9ecef; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #777; text-align: center; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Important Message from Fundeup Team</h1>
        <p>Hello {{username}},</p>
        <p>You have received a message from Fundedup team:</p>

        <div class="message-box">
            <p>{{messageContent}}</p>
        </div>

        <p>reply to this email (if applicable) for further action or details.</p>
        <p>Regards,<br>Fundedup</p>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>
